title: United Kingdom Imports - Woven Fabrics,Tufted Textile, Lace & Tapestries
description: Imports - Woven Fabrics,Tufted Textile, Lace & Tapestries in the United Kingdom increased to 20.25 GBP Million in September from 16.62 GBP Million in August of 2022. Imports - Woven Fabrics,Tufted Textile, Lace & Tap in the United Kingdom averaged 18.71 GBP Million from 2000 until 2022, reaching an all time high of 27.20 GBP Million in March of 2017 and a record low of 6.97 GBP Million in May of 2020.
